cdata.name: BitJob
cdata.desc:
Decentralized platform for Short-Term Online Jobs,Powered by a Cryptographic token economy.
bitJob Student Coin: STU will be purchased or sold with Traditional(Fiat) Money And with Cryptocurrencies.


BitJob will deploy blockchain technology in the global student community. Blockchain technology haslots ofpotential , butBitJobunderstands that smart education of consumers is necessary, in order for this to happen.BitJobis promoting the education to implement decentralization, through their labor market.
